{"cf_tracking_thunderbird_esr52": "---", "status": "RESOLVED", "cf_tracking_firefox60": "---", "cf_tracking_firefox61": "---", "cf_tracking_firefox62": "---", "creator": "bgrinstead@mozilla.com", "mentors_detail": [], "depends_on": [1447830], "cf_status_firefox_esr60": "---", "cf_user_story": "", "cf_tracking_firefox_relnote": "---", "platform": "Unspecified", "keywords": [], "cc_detail": [{"email": "bobbyholley@gmail.com", "id": 313730, "name": "bobbyholley@gmail.com", "real_name": "Bobby Holley (On Leave Until June 11th)"}, {"email": "bzbarsky@mit.edu", "id": 20209, "name": "bzbarsky@mit.edu", "real_name": "Boris Zbarsky [:bz] (Vacation Jun 16-24) (no decent commit message means r-)"}, {"email": "emilio@crisal.io", "id": 546716, "name": "emilio@crisal.io", "real_name": "Emilio Cobos \u00c1lvarez [:emilio]"}, {"email": "gandalf@aviary.pl", "id": 41270, "name": "gandalf@aviary.pl", "real_name": "Zibi Braniecki [:gandalf][:zibi]"}, {"email": "jorgk@jorgk.com", "id": 176914, "name": "jorgk@jorgk.com", "real_name": "Jorg K (GMT+2)"}, {"email": "richard.marti@gmail.com", "id": 282357, "name": "richard.marti@gmail.com", "real_name": "Richard Marti (:Paenglab)"}], "cf_last_resolved": "2018-03-14T10:07:53Z", "attachments": [{"creator": "bgrinstead@mozilla.com", "is_obsolete": 0, "is_patch": 0, "flags": [{"status": "+", "name": "review", "modification_date": "2018-03-13T21:08:21Z", "type_id": 4, "creation_date": "2018-03-12T20:24:59Z", "id": 1728521, "setter": "bzbarsky@mit.edu"}], "content_type": "text/x-review-board-request", "id": 8958174}], "votes": 0, "classification": "Components", "is_confirmed": true, "is_creator_accessible": true, "cf_has_regression_range": "---", "comment_count": 14, "comments": [{"text": "This is used when cloning a node to attach the binding before it's added to the DOM: https://searchfox.org/mozilla-central/rev/efce4ceddfbe5fe4e2d74f1aed93894bada9b273/dom/base/nsNodeUtils.cpp#725-742.\n\nAs far as I can tell, we don't rely on this in m-c. I did a try push with that code removed and the main failure I see is a XBL-specific test (dom/xbl/test/test_bug398492.xul): https://treeherder.mozilla.org/#/jobs?repo=try&revision=7637b0ecba8cdffccf243874e80e6af1f1b9c39c.", "author": "bgrinstead@mozilla.com", "id": 13112498, "time": "2018-03-07T22:26:11Z"}, {"text": "Jorg, last I checked there was c-c code that relied on this hackery.  Do you mind doing a c-c equivalent of that try push and seeing whether there is still fallout?", "author": "bzbarsky@mit.edu", "id": 13112562, "time": "2018-03-07T22:47:56Z"}, {"text": "I'm not sure what this is all about, where we would rely on this and what to look for, but here you go:\nhttps://treeherder.mozilla.org/#/jobs?repo=try-comm-central&revision=b29618c769e7142e6b71a3a72e74c5427688674c\nOne Xpcshell test failure currently expected due to bug 1443769.", "author": "jorgk@jorgk.com", "id": 13112695, "time": "2018-03-07T23:06:55Z"}, {"text": "> I'm not sure what this is all about\n\nThis is about removing the mechanism that force-applies XBL bindings to elements that are not in the document which happen to be clones of other elements.\n\n> where we would rely on this\n\nLast I checked, the mailcompose header bits relied on it...\n\nThank you for the try push!", "author": "bzbarsky@mit.edu", "id": 13112708, "time": "2018-03-07T23:13:52Z"}, {"text": "Looks like mozmill/session-store/test-session-store.js | test-session-store.js::test_message_pane_height_persistence failed.", "author": "jorgk@jorgk.com", "id": 13113385, "time": "2018-03-08T07:34:57Z"}, {"text": "Please ignore comment #4, this failure is new on the tree, see bug 1444045.", "author": "jorgk@jorgk.com", "id": 13113576, "time": "2018-03-08T09:49:38Z"}, {"text": "Great! Let's move forward here.\n\nDo the TB folks have a plan for when XBL/XUL start rapidly shrinking/changing and eventually go away? That's on the roadmap for 2018...", "author": "bobbyholley@gmail.com", "id": 13114351, "time": "2018-03-08T16:39:13Z"}, {"text": "> Do the TB folks have a plan for when XBL/XUL start rapidly shrinking/changing and eventually go away?\n\nAfaict, no.", "author": "bzbarsky@mit.edu", "id": 13114404, "time": "2018-03-08T16:52:57Z"}, {"text": "Created attachment 8958174\nBug 1443948 - Remove NODE_FORCE_XBL_BINDINGS;\n\nReview commit: https://reviewboard.mozilla.org/r/227120/diff/#index_header\nSee other reviews: https://reviewboard.mozilla.org/r/227120/", "author": "bgrinstead@mozilla.com", "id": 13122859, "time": "2018-03-12T18:45:52Z"}, {"text": "Comment on attachment 8958174\nBug 1443948 - Remove NODE_FORCE_XBL_BINDINGS;\n\nReview request updated; see interdiff: https://reviewboard.mozilla.org/r/227120/diff/1-2/", "author": "bgrinstead@mozilla.com", "id": 13123152, "time": "2018-03-12T20:24:59Z"}, {"text": "https://treeherder.mozilla.org/#/jobs?repo=try&revision=8b9d60159b8cb8df376d33afecb35c6e955c914d", "author": "bgrinstead@mozilla.com", "id": 13125431, "time": "2018-03-13T16:21:31Z"}, {"text": "Comment on attachment 8958174\nBug 1443948 - Remove NODE_FORCE_XBL_BINDINGS;\n\nhttps://reviewboard.mozilla.org/r/227120/#review233326\n\nr=me", "author": "bzbarsky@mit.edu", "id": 13126503, "time": "2018-03-13T21:08:21Z"}, {"text": "Pushed by bgrinstead@mozilla.com:\nhttps://hg.mozilla.org/integration/autoland/rev/dbf853820066\nRemove NODE_FORCE_XBL_BINDINGS;r=bz", "author": "pulsebot@bots.tld", "id": 13126536, "time": "2018-03-13T21:24:03Z"}, {"text": "https://hg.mozilla.org/mozilla-central/rev/dbf853820066", "author": "aiakab@mozilla.com", "id": 13127443, "time": "2018-03-14T10:07:53Z"}], "id": 1443948, "priority": "--", "cc": ["bobbyholley@gmail.com", "bzbarsky@mit.edu", "emilio@crisal.io", "gandalf@aviary.pl", "jorgk@jorgk.com", "richard.marti@gmail.com"], "cf_crash_signature": "", "version": "unspecified", "is_cc_accessible": true, "cf_tracking_firefox_esr52": "---", "see_also": [], "cf_tracking_thunderbird_esr60": "---", "cf_platform_rel": "---", "product": "Core", "cf_fx_iteration": "---", "